    • assignSeat

      public Seat assignSeat(int row, int column)
      Assigns a seat in this seating layout. Sets a seat in given row and column to be OCCUPIED for a showing.
      Parameters:
      row - Row number of the seat to be assigned.
      column - Column number of the seat to be assigned.
      Returns:
      Returns assigned seat if UNOCCUPIED seat is successfully set to OCCUPIED, else returns null if seat is already OCCUPIED.

    • unassignSeat

      public Seat unassignSeat(int row, int column)
      Unassigns a seat in this seating layout. Sets a seat in given row and column to be UNOCCUPIED for a showing.
      Parameters:
      row - Row number of the seat to be unassigned.
      column - Column number of the seat to be unassigned.
      Returns:
      Returns assigned seat if OCCUPIED seat is successfully set to UNOCCUPIED, else returns null if seat is already UNOCCUPIED.
